title: [1508521049] Rum-Infused Panna Cotta with Pomegranate Glaze - Gordon Ramsay
description:
For those who don't like Christmas pudding, Gordon's rum-infused panna cotta is a beautiful and simple solution. An easy recipe that can be prepared ahead of time and will cleanse the palate after the big Christmas meal.
